---
// The Challenge section for Professional Services industry page
---

<section id="challenge" class="cre-challenge-section">
  <div class="cre-challenge-container">
    <span class="section-label">THE CHALLENGE</span>
    <h2 class="cre-challenge-headline">
      Speed vs. process in commercial real estate
    </h2>
    <p class="cre-challenge-subheadline">
      Professional services moves fast out of necessity. Client deadlines are immovable. Budget cycles are tight. But most firms are still running on spreadsheets, manual processes, and disconnected systems that create project delays and margin leakage.
    </p>

    <!-- Highlight Box -->
    <div class="cre-highlight-box">
      <p class="cre-highlight-text">
        "The average professional services firm loses 15-25% of potential profit because they can't allocate resources efficiently and track time accurately."
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Challenge List -->
    <div class="cre-challenge-list-wrapper">
      <ul class="cre-challenge-list">
        <li><strong>Project scoping is inconsistent</strong> across email, documents, and spreadsheets—making it impossible to track scope creep and understand true project profitability.</li>
        <li><strong>Resource allocation is reactive</strong> instead of planned, forcing teams to manually assign people to projects and shuffle resources last-minute as projects slip and priorities change.</li>
        <li><strong>Time tracking and billing is disconnected</strong>, requiring consultants to manually log hours in separate systems, creating gaps and delays in invoicing that extend cash flow cycles.</li>
        <li><strong>Project performance is opaque</strong>, requiring manual status reports and retrospective analysis to understand what actually happened versus what was planned.</li>
        <li><strong>Capacity planning is impossible</strong> because visibility into project pipelines, resource availability, and team bandwidth lives in different systems—forcing expensive bench time and missed utilization.</li>
        <li><strong>Client collaboration breaks down</strong> when project communication, deliverables, and feedback live across email, shared drives, and messaging apps instead of a unified workspace.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Stat Cards -->
    <div class="cre-stat-cards">
      <div class="cre-stat-card">
        <div class="cre-stat-number">15-25%</div>
        <div class="cre-stat-label">profit lost</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cre-stat-card">
        <div class="cre-stat-number">30+ hrs</div>
        <div class="cre-stat-label">monthly admin overhead</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cre-stat-card">
        <div class="cre-stat-number">5-7 days</div>
        <div class="cre-stat-label">invoicing delay</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-challenge-section {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    padding: clamp(30px, 4vw, 50px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-challenge-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-challenge-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-challenge-subheadline {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .cre-highlight-box {
    background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.05);
    border-left: 4px solid #0EA5E9;
    padding: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .cre-highlight-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #000000;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cre-challenge-list-wrapper {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .cre-challenge-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .cre-challenge-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 32px;
    font-size: 17px; /* Increased from 16px for better readability */
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  }

  .cre-challenge-list li::before {
    content: '−';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #0EA5E9;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .cre-challenge-list li strong {
    font-size: 17px; /* Match parent font size */
    color: #000000;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .cre-stat-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .cre-stat-card {
    background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.2);
    padding: 32px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-stat-card:hover {
    background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.4);
  }

  .cre-stat-number {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #0EA5E9;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .cre-stat-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-challenge-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cre-challenge-list li {
      font-size: 16px; /* Slightly smaller on tablet */
    }

    .cre-challenge-list li strong {
      font-size: 16px; /* Match tablet size */
    }

    .cre-stat-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-challenge-section {
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-challenge-list li {
      font-size: 15px; /* Original size on mobile for space efficiency */
    }

    .cre-challenge-list li strong {
      font-size: 15px; /* Match mobile size */
    }

    .cre-highlight-box {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .cre-stat-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>

